---

<Layout title="Chypre Collection | AETHERIA" lang="en" description="Explore the AETHERIA Chypre Collection. The architectural heart of perfumery — where citrus brightness meets the dark forest-floor depth of oakmoss. Bergamot, Patchouli, and Oakmoss extraits.">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav
    data-mobile-nav
    class="sticky top-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center h-[100px] px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-outline-variant"
  >
    <div
      class="font-display-xl text-headline-sm tracking-widest text-primary flex items-center"
    >
      <a href="/">AETHERIA</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-10 items-center">
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary border-b border-primary pb-1 transition-colors duration-300"
        href="/collections"
      >Collections</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Scent Notes</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >The Archive</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
        href="#"
      >Bespoke</a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">search</span>
      </button>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">shopping_bag</span>
      </button>
      <button class="touch-target hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
      </button>
      <button class="hamburger md:hidden touch-target" data-toggle-mobile aria-label="Menu">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="mobile-drawer" data-mobile-drawer>
    <a href="/collections" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Collections</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Scent Notes</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">The Archive</a>
    <a href="#" class="font-label-caps text-lg tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity">Bespoke</a>
    <hr class="border-outline-variant my-4" />
    <a href="/" class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-overlay" data-mobile-overlay></div>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="relative w-full min-h-screen md:h-[819px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div
        class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-[3000ms] hover:scale-105"
        style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCD72KE76v-SYk1kRTZEizOvNKojYq1E7rNXyij3pWPfKcwuGehCKlnlHNCH-nO6fYMLbVIB1RR_vpSu29mYRFrbYpLZFilopXigBSZTD_9p5keIJoo7YnLoMpYgfi0C6IutttEwH42XZs3LYTmsAkSGV_QP-Q79AgZajty_gf75eW_z1xb8xPXUJsknxv7ODJGGRfJcqFnaeDhxF9YEjq6U6tOYos7yE-cFFEscDU8q_nEzmvAf5aQ4cm1k2Jv3UKfFP4jDCceUNZt')"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-4xl">
      <p
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-primary mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase"
      >Category Exploration</p>
      <h1
        class="font-display-xl text-headline-lg md:text-display-xl text-white mb-6"
      >
        Chypre Collection
      </h1>
      <p
        class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-white/90 max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed"
      >
        The architectural heart of perfumery. Defined by the sophisticated
        tension between citrus brightness and the dark, forest-floor depth of
        oakmoss.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <button
          class="bg-white text-black px-10 py-4 font-label-caps text-label-caps hover:bg-tertiary-fixed transition-colors duration-500"
        >Discover More</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <!-- Collection Description -->
  <section
    class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center">
      <div class="md:col-span-5" data-reveal>
        <span
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant border-b border-tertiary-fixed-dim pb-1 mb-8 inline-block"
        >THE NOTES</span>
        <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-8">
          The tripartite structure of the earth.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Aetheria's Chypre scents are a study in artisanal contrast. We source
          our oakmoss from the deep forests of central Europe, pairing it with
          bergamot from the first pressing in Calabria. This collection represents
          the 'Gilded Earth'—fragrances that feel as structured as a tailored
          coat and as organic as the roots of a cedar tree.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div
            class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-2 group cursor-pointer"
          >
            <span
              class="font-label-caps text-label-caps group-hover:text-tertiary-fixed-dim transition-colors"
            >Bergamot</span>
            <span class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant"
            >Calabria</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-2 group cursor-pointer"
          >
            <span
              class="font-label-caps text-label-caps group-hover:text-tertiary-fixed-dim transition-colors"
            >Oakmoss</span>
            <span class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant"
            >Auvergne</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-2 group cursor-pointer"
          >
            <span
              class="font-label-caps text-label-caps group-hover:text-tertiary-fixed-dim transition-colors"
            >Patchouli</span>
            <span class="font-caption text-caption text-on-surface-variant"
            >Sumatra</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="md:col-start-7 md:col-span-6 relative aspect-[4/5]"
        data-reveal
        style="transition-delay: 200ms;"
      >
        <div
          class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center shadow-2xl"
          style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDjbWvAKhvKDu4PY_c8UFuSqbNclqChb3HfQGB4EK3hvWRrnrUQ3092xV17UK79Fv-ZLO8Xxh7er4NDw17C4sHYNEyfEfJx7Rdap3dgSTZENMWn5lJUH-3jswQymZm2NH_lDY6sAwUCzaUPx0ik5R2s7mmSnrcgrLf-8TRWqDj5xOfR2GYqVrnLILPox3laf66yuB8iJ8ZlSZQiPuB_ng8TjOlSvSrp3IdAa9orDIR1jB6oRotcp2hLcGsF0xsP3P23rSfxg4OP2C_4')"
        ></div>
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-48 h-48 bg-surface-container-high hidden md:block -z-10 border border-outline-variant"
        ></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Product Grid -->
  <section
    class="pb-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-20">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md">Selected Extraits</h3>
        <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mt-2">
          6 ARCHIVAL FORMULATIONS
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6 md:mt-0">
        <button class="font-label-caps text-label-caps border-b border-primary"
        >Filter</button>
        <button class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant"
        >Sort By</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-gutter gap-y-16">
      {products.map((product) => (
        <div class="group" data-reveal>
          <div
            class="aspect-[1/1] bg-surface-container overflow-hidden mb-6 relative"
          >
            <img
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
              src={product.img}
              alt={product.name}
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
            ></div>
            <button
              class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md px-6 py-3 font-label-caps text-[10px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 max-md:opacity-100 max-md:translate-y-0"
            >
              QUICK ADD
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p
              class="font-label-caps text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant mb-1 tracking-widest"
            >
              {product.badge}
            </p>
            <h4 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2">
              {product.name}
            </h4>
            <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
              {product.price}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Bespoke CTA -->
  <section
    class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="font-display-xl text-headline-lg md:text-headline-lg mb-8">
        The Alchemy of Self
      </h2>
      <p
        class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-inverse-on-surface/80 mb-12"
      >
        Chypre is a personal dialogue. If our curated archival scents do not
        speak to your soul, our Master Perfumer is available for bespoke
        formulation.
      </p>
      <button
        class="bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 font-label-caps text-label-caps hover:bg-tertiary-fixed transition-all duration-500"
      >
        BOOK A CONSULTATION
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer
    class="w-full py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-background border-t border-outline-variant flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-12"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
      <div
        class="font-display-xl text-headline-sm tracking-widest text-primary mb-4"
      >
        AETHERIA
      </div>
      <p class="font-label-caps text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant">
        THE ARCHITECTS OF OLFACTION
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10">
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >Privacy</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >Terms</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >Shipping</a>
      <a
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors"
        href="#"
      >Contact</a>
    </div>
    <div class="text-right">
      <p
        class="font-label-caps text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant tracking-widest"
      >
        © 2024 AETHERIA. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
